Privacy Policy
Advertising
ColorfulCalc may collect and pass to third parties geolocation information linked to your mobile device or advertising identifiers and may do so when you use the app. That information may be used by Third parties to customize ads in this app or in other apps. The ads displayed in the app may transmit clicks and page views. This information helps generate revenue, allowing the app to be offered for free. The information is anonymous and cannot be used to identify ColorfulCalc users. ColorfulCalc allows third party companies to collect usage information that does not identify an individual user. These third parties may use cookies, pixels, or other technologies to collect and use non-personally identifiable information during your visits in order to provide advertisments that better fit your interests. If you do not want this information to be linked to your device you may opt out of interest-based or personalized advertising by going to your devices' settings.

Analytics
ColorfulCalc uses Apple analytics to collect statistics on app crashes and usage. This information helps to fix issues when encountered. This data is collected anonymously and cannot be used to identify users.

